queries.sql: SELECT matakuliah.kode_prodi, prodi.nama_prodi, matakuliah.kode_matakuliah, matakuliah.kode_konsentrasi, tb_konsentrasi.konsentrasi, matakuliah.nama_matakuliah, matakuliah.sks, matakuliah.id_kurikulum, mcpmk.idcpmk, mcpmk.cpmk, if(rplcpmk.idcpmk is NULL,0,1) AS status_rpl FROM matakuliah LEFT JOIN tb_konsentrasi ON matakuliah.kode_konsentrasi = tb_konsentrasi.kode_konsentrasi left join prodi on matakuliah.kode_prodi = prodi.kode_prodi left join (select * from master_cpmk )mcpmk on matakuliah.kode_matakuliah = mcpmk.kode_matakuliah LEFT JOIN (select * from mk_cpmk)rplcpmk on matakuliah.kode_matakuliah = rplcpmk.kode_matakuliah and rplcpmk.ta_akademik='20231' WHERE (jenis_matakuliah = '1' or jenis_matakuliah = '2') and mcpmk.idcpmk is not null group by matakuliah.kode_matakuliah
